  1. Different QNR selection (faster?)
  2. Adds Euler test
  3. Khashin:  (1+q)^n = 1-q  or (2+q)^n = 2-q
     Phatak:   (1+q)^n - 1 - q^n = 0  =>  (1+q)^n = 1 + q^n
